<p itemprop="description">A trainee business architect supports more senior business architect roles and receives training on business architecture tasks. They learn to understand organizational structures and business processes while working under supervision.</p>

<section class="role-details">
    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Support other business architects in producing clear business architecture outputs</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Participate in workshops and meetings with stakeholders in the organisation</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Learn and apply basic business architecture principles and methods</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Assist in documenting business processes and organizational structures</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Support data gathering and analysis for business architecture projects</li>
    </ul>
</section>

